# Event Hunter Skill

## What You Do
Discover upcoming startup events, pitch competitions, demo days, conferences, and hackathons. Extract attendee/speaker lists for founder outreach. Generate event-specific outreach campaigns.

## Event Sources (Search Priority)

### 1. Pitch Competitions & Demo Days
- Y Combinator Demo Day (batch schedules)
- TechCrunch Disrupt
- Launch Festival
- Startup Battlefield
- University pitch competitions
- Local accelerator demo days

### 2. Conferences
- Web Summit, Collision, SXSW
- SaaStr Annual
- TechCrunch Early Stage
- Founder-focused unconferences
- Industry-specific conferences (AI, FinTech, HealthTech)

### 3. Hackathons
- Major League Hacking events
- Corporate-sponsored hackathons
- AI/ML hackathons (common source of technical founders)

### 4. Meetups & Local Events
- Startup Grind chapters
- Founder meetups in major cities
- Tech meetup groups
- Co-working space events

### 5. Online Events
- Product Hunt launches (daily)
- Twitter/X Spaces about fundraising
- LinkedIn Live events
- Clubhouse rooms (if still active)
- Discord community events

## How to Search

### Browser-Based Discovery
- Browse eventbrite.com â€” search "startup pitch", "demo day", "founder"
- Browse meetup.com â€” search startup groups in SF, NYC, Austin, Boston
- Browse lu.ma â€” startup and founder events
- Browse partiful.com â€” tech community events
- Check accelerator websites for demo day dates

### Web Search Queries
```
"demo day 2026" startup
"pitch competition" {month} 2026
startup conference {city} 2026
founder meetup {city}
hackathon {vertical} 2026
```

## Output Format

Save to `workspace/events/YYYY-MM-{month}-events.md`:

```markdown
# Startup Events â€” {Month YYYY}

## Upcoming Events

### 1. {Event Name}
- **Date**: {date}
- **Location**: {city / online}
- **Type**: Pitch Competition / Demo Day / Conference / Hackathon / Meetup
- **URL**: {link}
- **Estimated Founders**: {N}
- **Relevant Verticals**: {AI, SaaS, etc.}
- **Outreach Opportunity**:
  - [ ] Attendee list available
  - [ ] Speaker list available
  - [ ] Can sponsor/partner
  - [ ] Can attend and network
- **Action Plan**: {how to leverage this event}
- **Priority**: HIGH / MEDIUM / LOW

### 2. ...
```

## Event-Based Outreach

### Pre-Event (1-2 weeks before)
```
Subject: "See you at {event}?"

Hi {first_name},

Noticed {company} is presenting at {event}. Congrats!

Quick idea: founders who upload a 90-second pitch video
to PitchTok before demo days get 5-10x more investor
pre-meetings. Takes < 5 min.

Want me to send the link?

{sender_name}
```

### Post-Event (1-2 days after)
```
Subject: "Congrats on {event}!"

Hi {first_name},

Great seeing {company} at {event}! {Specific compliment
about their pitch/presentation}.

If you're looking to extend that momentum â€” PitchTok
lets investors who weren't at {event} discover your
pitch through short video. {X} investors active this week.

Worth a 5-minute try?

{sender_name}
```

## Weekly Event Scan
- Every Monday: search for events in the next 4 weeks
- Add new events to the calendar
- Generate pre-event outreach for events in 1-2 weeks
- Generate post-event outreach for events that just ended
